race.comment: SATAY CHICKEN (1) resumes and flies fresh. Brings strong form from better races and has trialled well at Moree. Suited and the 3kg claim brings him right into it. Tough to roll. ADALIE (10) settled back and looked in need of the outing here first-up. She is also back in grade and her second-up record is sharp. Maps for a soft run and can make the finish. BEE TWO (5) didn't get into it in Open grade last time but his placing here prior was a decent effort. He's on a quick backup and can go better. KWAMI (7)  hasn't fired in his three runs for the new yard but showed plenty early on. Maps well and he can get into the money in this lineup.
